- "Fruits of its performance" refers to the average performance metrics (run time complexity, sample accuracy, general accuracy, and resources utilized) of the algorithms;
- "History of its evaluations" refers to the count of evaluations and their statuses for each algorithm;
- "Evolution of its versions" refers to the total number of versions and the number of current versions for each algorithm.

