- "Blossomed like the most resilient flowers" metaphorically describes the algorithms that have performed the best under the given criteria;
- "Recent comparative analysis" refers to any analyses conducted after January 1, 2022.

- "Top 3 in terms of average input length" refers to the algorithms with the highest average input length;
- "Total resource utilization" includes CPU, memory, disk, GPU, and network usage;
- "Average total resource utilization" is the mean of the total resource utilization across all algorithms.

- 'blossomed into the realm of classification' refers to algorithms in the 'classification' category;
